Prepared in clean and hygienic conditions, following the same five decade old recipe(since 1963), this winter sesame delight uses the finest raw materials, be it refined sugar from Bareilly or jaggery from Meerut. Other ingredients include sesame seeds, pistachio and desi ghee.

Storage instructions: Store at room temperature in an air-tight container, Do Not Refrigerate

Description

Prepared in clean and hygienic conditions, following the same five decade old recipe(since 1963), this winter sesame delight uses the finest raw materials, be it refined sugar from Bareilly or jaggery from Meerut. Other ingredients include sesame seeds, pistachio and desi ghee.

Storage instructions: Store at room temperature in an air-tight container, Do Not Refrigerate.
